{"type":"user","uuid":"14aba0b4-3e6a-4518-8b90-40956340856c","session_id":"b2229cc3-f35d-4fe4-8e7e-67c19086b8f2","message":{"content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_90a84efff7794d44864563c2","content":[{"type":"text","text":"   1Ôćĺ{\n   2Ôćĺ  \"name\": \"prizm-dev-team\",\n   3Ôćĺ  \"description\": \"PrizmKit-integrated Multi-Agent software development team. 4 specialized agents (Coordinator, PM, Dev, Reviewer) following PrizmKit spec-driven workflow with 7-phase pipeline and 4 checkpoints.\",\n   4Ôćĺ  \"createdAt\": 1773251367290,\n   5Ôćĺ  \"leadAgentId\": \"team-lead@prizm-dev-team\",\n   6Ôćĺ  \"leadSessionId\": \"\",\n   7Ôćĺ  \"members\": [\n   8Ôćĺ    {\n   9Ôćĺ      \"agentId\": \"team-lead@prizm-dev-team\",\n  10Ôćĺ      \"name\": \"team-lead\",\n  11Ôćĺ      \"agentType\": \"prizm-dev-team-coordinator\",\n  12Ôćĺ      \"joinedAt\": 1773251367290,\n  13Ôćĺ      \"tmuxPaneId\": \"\",\n  14Ôćĺ      \"cwd\": \"\",\n  15Ôćĺ      \"subscriptions\": []\n  16Ôćĺ    },\n  17Ôćĺ    {\n  18Ôćĺ      \"agentId\": \"coordinator@prizm-dev-team\",\n  19Ôćĺ      \"name\": \"coordinator\",\n  20Ôćĺ      \"agentType\": \"prizm-dev-team-coordinator\",\n  21Ôćĺ      \"prompt\": \"You are the Coordinator Agent of the prizm-dev-team. Orchestrate the 7-phase pipeline (init Ôćĺ specify+plan+tasks Ôćĺ analyze Ôćĺ implement Ôćĺ review Ôćĺ summarize Ôćĺ commit). Manage checkpoints CP-0 through CP-3, coordinate PM/Dev/Reviewer agents. Follow PrizmKit workflow.\",\n  22Ôćĺ      \"joinedAt\": 1773251367291,\n  23Ôćĺ      \"tmuxPaneId\": \"\",\n  24Ôćĺ      \"cwd\": \"\",\n  25Ôćĺ      \"subscriptions\": [\n  26Ôćĺ        \"*\"\n  27Ôćĺ      ]\n  28Ôćĺ    },\n  29Ôćĺ    {\n  30Ôćĺ      \"agentId\": \"pm@prizm-dev-team\",\n  31Ôćĺ      \"name\": \"pm\",\n  32Ôćĺ      \"agentType\": \"prizm-dev-team-pm\",\n  33Ôćĺ      \"prompt\": \"You are the PM Agent of the prizm-dev-team. In a single session, use prizmkit.specify/clarify/plan/tasks to create spec.md, plan.md, and tasks.md