- Integration tests in `tests/integration/f003-plan-ingestion.integration.test.js`\n 114Ôćĺ\n 115Ôćĺ### Acceptance Criteria Met\n 116Ôćĺ\n 117Ôćĺ- US-1: Upload Plan File - Telegram document message handling with auto-type detection\n 118Ôćĺ- US-2: Schema Validation - Ajv-based validation with field-level error messages\n 119Ôćĺ- US-3: Version Management - Timestamp-based versioning with use/rollback commands\n 120Ôćĺ- US-4: Plan Status Query - Status command showing version info and content summary\n 121Ôćĺ- US-5: Plan Integrity Protection - Validation precedes save, current version preserved on error\n 122Ôćĺ- US-6: Pipeline Integration - resolvePlanListPath() for dynamic plan path resolution\n 123Ôćĺ\n 124Ôćĺ### Commands Implemented\n 125Ôćĺ\n 126Ôćĺ| Command | Subcommands | Description |\n 127Ôćĺ|---------|-------------|-------------|\n 128Ôćĺ| `/plan` | status, versions, use, rollback, validate | Manage plan files |\n 129Ôćĺ\n 130Ôćĺ### Verification\n 131Ôćĺ\n 132Ôćĺ- Code review: PASS_WITH_WARNINGS\n 133Ôćĺ- All 18 tasks completed\n 134Ôćĺ- Unit tests: 19 passing\n 135Ôćĺ- Integration tests: 10 passing\n 136Ôćĺ\n 137Ôćĺ---\n 138Ôćĺ\n 139Ôćĺ## F-004: Pipeline Process Controller\n 140Ôćĺ\n 141Ôćĺ**Status:** completed\n 142Ôćĺ**Completion Date:** 2026-03-12\n 143Ôćĺ\n 144Ôćĺ### Deliverables\n 145Ôćĺ\n 146Ôćĺ- `src/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.js` - File-based lock management with PID validation\n 147Ôćĺ- `src/pipeline-infra/state-manager.js` - State file reading/writing for daemon and pipeline state\n 148Ôćĺ- `src/pipeline-infra/error-codes.js` - Extended with 6 new error codes for F-004\n 149Ôćĺ- `src/pipeline-infra/path-policy.js` - Extended with lock/state path resolvers\n 150Ôćĺ- `src/services/pipeline-controller.js` - Unified pipeline control API with concurrency protection\n 151Ôćĺ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/pipeline.js` - Updated to use pipeline-controller\n 152Ôćĺ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/status.js` - Updated to use pipeline-controller\n 153Ôćĺ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/logs.js` - Updated to use pipeline-controller\n 154Ôćĺ- `src/bot/commands/handlers/stop.js` - Updated to use pipeline-controller\n 155Ôćĺ- Unit tests in `tests/pipeline-infra/lock-manager.test.js` and `tests/pipeline-infra/state-manager.test.js`\n 156Ôćĺ- Unit tests in `tests/services/pipeline-controller.test.js`\n 157Ôćĺ- Integration tests in `tests/integration/f004-pipeline-controller.integration.test.js`\n 158Ôćĺ\n 159Ôćĺ### Acceptance Criteria Met\n 160Ôćĺ\n 161Ôćĺ- US-1: Unified Pipeline Start - startPipeline with daemon/foreground modes, lock acquisition\n 162Ôćĺ- US-2: Pipeline Stop - stopPipeline with ALREADY_STOPPED handling, lock release\n 163Ôćĺ- US-3: Target Retry - retryTarget with validation and mode support\n 164Ôćĺ- US-4: Run Single Feature - runSingle without lock (independent execution)\n 165Ôćĺ- US-5: Status Query - getStatus with daemon/pipeline state, lastResult\n 166Ôćĺ- US-6: Logs Query - getLogs with line limit, missing file handling\n 167Ôćĺ- US-7: Concurrency Protection - lock-manager with stale lock cleanup, forceUnlock\n 168Ôćĺ- US-8: Error Mapping - Consistent error codes with hint/context fields\n 169Ôćĺ- US-9: Telegram Handler Integration - All handlers updated to use pipeline-controller\n 170Ôćĺ\n 171Ôćĺ### Error Codes Added\n 172Ôćĺ\n 173Ôćĺ| Code | Description |\n 174Ôćĺ|------|-------------|\n 175Ôćĺ| LOCK_ACQUISITION_FAILED | Pipeline already running |\n 176Ôćĺ| ALREADY_STOPPED | Pipeline not running |\n 177Ôćĺ| PIPELINE_NOT_RUNNING | No active pipeline |\n 178Ôćĺ| INVALID_TARGET | Missing or invalid target ID |\n 179Ôćĺ| TARGET_NOT_RETRYABLE | Target state not retryable |\n 180Ôćĺ| DAEMON_START_FAILED | Failed to start daemon |\n 181Ôćĺ\n 182Ôćĺ### Key Decisions\n 183Ôćĺ\n 184Ôćĺ- D1: File lock + PID validation for concurrency protection (no external dependencies)\n 185Ôćĺ- D2: Separate lock-manager module for single responsibility\n 186Ôćĺ- D3: Reuse existing state files (backward compatible)\n 187Ôćĺ- D4: Ne