ing - Commit history stored in session, /commits command\n- US-5: High-Risk Commit Protection - amend/force require admin + confirmation\n\n### Commands Implemented\n\n| Command | Aliases | Min Role | Description |\n|---------|---------|----------|-------------|\n| `/commit` | `/c` | operator | Commit changes |\n| `/commit --amend` | ÔÇö | admin | Amend last commit (requires confirmation) |\n| `/commit --force` | ÔÇö | admin | Skip validation (requires confirmation) |\n| `/commits` | `/history` | viewer | View session commit history |\n\n### Key Decisions\n\n- D1: Use simple-git library to avoid shell injection risks\n- D2: Pre-commit validation includes pipeline and test status checks\n- D3: Commit records stored in session state file\n- D4: Reuse F-006 confirmation mechanism for amend/force\n- D5: GitService designed for mockability in tests\n\n### Verification\n\n- All 45 tasks completed\n- Unit tests: 47+ passing\n- Integration tests: 10+ passing\n- NFR: All tests pass with npm test","old_string":"- Code review: PASS\n- 37 of 40 tasks completed (core functionality complete)\n- Test suite: 200+ tests passing\n- NFR-1: Unit tests < 10s, Integration tests < 60s"}}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":137969,"output_tokens":771,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_0205ff99439e49bba2f8aa57","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:30:52.944Z","_requestId":"b07a63a169934f4593711d9842f5a228"}
