{"type":"assistant","uuid":"20260312053124e54e024b3bad4230","session_id":"b2229cc3-f35d-4fe4-8e7e-67c19086b8f2","message":{"id":"20260312053124e54e024b3bad4230","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## F-008 Commit Workflow Integration - Implementation Complete Ôťů\n\nAll 46 tasks have been successfully implemented following TDD methodology. Here's a summary:\n\n### Deliverables\n\n**Services:**\n- `src/services/git-service.js` - Git operations wrapper using simple-git library\n  - `getStatus()`, `isClean()`, `getChangedFiles()`, `commit()`, `amendCommit()`, `getLastCommit()`, `getCommitLog()`, `getShortHash()`\n- `src/services/commit-service.js` - Commit workflow orchestration\n  - `validatePreConditions()`, `commit()`, `recordCommit()`, `getSessionCommits()`, `checkPipelineStatus()`, `checkTestStatus()`, `buildCommitMessage()`, `getErrorSuggestion()`\n- `src/services/session-store.js` - Extended with commit tracking\n  - `addCommit()`, `getCommits()`, `getLastCommit()`\n\n**Command Handlers:**\n- `src/bot/commands/handlers/commit.js` - `/commit` command with `--message`, `--amend`, `--force` flags\n- `src/bot/commands/handlers/commits.js` - `/commits` command for session history\n\n**Security Integration:**\n- Permission matrix extended: `commit` (operator), `commit-amend`/`commit-force` (admin)\n- Confirmation flow for high-risk operations (amend/force)\n- Audit logging for all commit operations\n\n**Tests:**\n- `tests/services/git-service.test.js` - 23 unit tests passing\n- `tests/services/commit-service.test.js` - 24 unit tests passing\n- `tests/bot/commands/handlers/commit.test.js` - Handler tests\n- `tests/bot/commands/handlers/commits.test.js` - Handler tests\n- Integration tests in `tests/integration/`\n\n### Commands Implemented\n\n| Command | Aliases | Min Role | Description |\n|---------|---------|----------|-------------|\n| `/commit` | `/c` | operator | Commit code changes |\n| `/commit --amend` | ÔÇö | admin | Amend last commit (requires confirmation) |\n| `/commit --force` | ÔÇö | admin | Skip validation (requires confirmation) |\n| `/commits` | `/history` | viewer | View session commit history |\n\n### Key Design Decisions\n\n- **D1:** Use simple-git library to avoid shell injection risks\n- **D2:** Pre-commit validation includes pipeline and test status checks\n- **D3:** Commit records stored in session state file\n- **D4:** Reuse F-006 confirmation mechanism for amend/force\n- **D5:** GitService designed for mockability in tests"}],"model":"glm-5.0","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":140675,"output_tokens":594,"cache_creation_input_tokens":null,"cache_read_input_tokens":null,"cache_creation":null,"server_tool_use":null,"service_tier":null}},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_0205ff99439e49bba2f8aa57","__timestamp":"2026-03-11T21:31:38.657Z","_requestId":"b07a63a169934f4593711d9842f5a228"}
