endation:** Investigate test file import chain for circular dependencies\n\n### LOW Priority (3)\n\n#### L-1: Missing JSDoc for Internal Functions\n- **File:** `commit.js:181` - executeCommit()\n- **Issue:** Internal function lacks JSDoc documentation\n- **Impact:** Minor - code is self-documenting\n\n#### L-2: Session ID Derivation Could Be Centralized\n- **File:** `commit.js:185`, `commits.js:44`\n- **Issue:** Session ID logic duplicated: `ctx?.chat?.id?.toString() || session-${userId}`\n- **Impact:** Minor - DRY violation\n\n#### L-3: Timestamp Formatting Duplicated\n- **File:** `commits.js:103-123` - formatTimestamp()\n- **Issue:** Similar formatting exists in other handlers\n- **Impact:** Minor - could be extracted to utility\n\n---\n\n## Plan Adherence Check\n\n| Plan Component | Implementation Status |\n|----------------|----------------------|\n| GitService (C-1) | Ôťů Fully implemented |\n| CommitService (C-2) | Ôťů Fully implemented |\n| Commit Handler (C-3) | Ôťů Fully implemented |\n| Commits Handler (C-4) | Ôťů Fully implemented |\n| Pre-Commit Validation API (I-1) | Ôťů Matches plan design |\n| Commit Execution API (I-2) | Ôťů Matches plan design |\n| Session Commit Tracking (I-3) | Ôťů Matches plan design |\n| Permission Matrix | Ôťů Matches plan (commit=operator, amend/force=admin) |\n\n---\n\n## Security Review\n\n| Check | Status | Notes |\n|-------|--------|-------|\n| Shell Injection Prevention | Ôťů | Uses simple-git library (D1) |\n| Permission Checks | Ôťů | isAdmin() for amend/force |\n| Confirmation Flow | Ôťů | F-006 ConfirmationManager reused |\n| Audit Logging | Ôťů | All operations logged |\n| Input Validation | Ôťů | sanitizeParam() for message |\n| Message Length Limit | Ôťů | 500 char limit enforced |\n\n---\n\n## Test Coverage Summary\n\n| Test File | Tests | Status |\n|-----------|-------|--------|\n| `tests/services/git-service.test.js` | 23 | Ôťů PASS |\n| `tests/services/commit-service.test.js` | ~20 | Ôťů PASS |\n| `tests/bot/co